POKÉMON ZOO AMERICA

“Step Into the World You Imagined as a Kid.”

A next-generation immersive entertainment park combining:

* theme park
* living AI world
* collectible museum
* AR/MMO gameplay
* safari attraction
* esports arena
* social hub
* retail ecosystem
* nostalgia cathedral

Unlike traditional theme parks, Pokémon Zoo America is not just a place you visit.

It is a persistent world you participate in.

⸻

CORE VISION

Create the closest thing possible to:

“What it would feel like if Pokémon existed in real life.”

Not mascots.
Not static rides.
Not screens.

A living, reactive ecosystem.

Every guest becomes a Trainer.

